The paper deals with explaining neural networks, which is a common topic in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses adversarial attacks on explanations, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper discusses the importance of creating explanations that are understandable to humans, which is a topic in human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
